{"tid":1758403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆再教育營受害者揭慘況   高呼「習近平萬歲」才能吃飯","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:38:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1389bec44de6cf819d8dad2dc2731cbc6e922c4a","tid":1758403,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"中國政府在新疆大規模設立「再教育營」，關押超過百萬名維吾爾人、哈薩克人和穆斯林。曾被關押在新疆「集中營」的「學員」向外媒揭露內情，他們甚至要高喊精神口號「感恩習近平、習近平萬歲」才能吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，北京當局聲稱「再教育營」是為反恐目的推行的「職訓中心」，凡入住「再教育營」的學員均爲「自願」接受職業培訓和教育轉化，但24日被國際調查記者同盟（ICIJ）曝光的官方文件「中國電文」披露了在這些營地的囚犯被關押、灌輸思想和懲罰的實情，直接打臉中國官方發佈的不實消息。<br />\n<br />\n與ICIJ合作的多家外媒採訪到參與其中的人員及受害者說法，一位「職訓中心」前講師透露，設施裡每個角落都有配槍警察，根本無法逃走。被關押的人會被強迫認罪，認的罪還要重到管理單位滿意，一舉一動都會被打分數。<br />\n<br />\n這位前講師說，她一遍又一遍教導學員「沒有共產黨，我就無法生存」、「共產黨向我展示了活著的唯一方法」。她說，中國政府的目標就是讓少數民族漢族化，「這不是要教導他們，這是要徹底摧毀他們」。<br />\n<br />\n曾被關押於「再教育營」的學員則透露，再教育營中，起床就要唱中國國歌，用餐前也要齊聲高喊「感恩習近平、習近平萬歲」才能用餐，一個月只能冷水洗澡2分鐘，他們也被告知，若有信仰，就信中國的佛教，不要去信伊斯蘭這種海外來的傳染病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2990305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2990305&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=58376cc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2990305&h=043b1a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2990305</a>"},{"pid":"47e26492e0779d0c2b1d87fc85308bd5e3975b77","tid":1758403,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5ce575c77c0670bf2808bbe21ca29275ae8f248","tid":1758403,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5e292106639dfad4855d9aaa6f8253490e49749","tid":1758403,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0637d338ab5d5d8f2d160e87f4631dbce3b127f4","tid":1758403,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"諗起老衲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2571462b892b9292d051aaad8d28652a12cf5c","tid":1758403,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ce575c77c0670bf2808bbe21ca29275ae8f248","tid":1758403,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceaee8d01eca11296851a8f43bbc989a69224e0","tid":1758403,"uid":194324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ce575c77c0670bf2808bbe21ca29275ae8f248","tid":1758403,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"link呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f67d8b0866f0ae2accd4ba446bd9fcf21377740","tid":1758403,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime